com.vmware.connectors.common.payloads.response

Class CardAction.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.connectors.common.payloads.response.CardAction.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    CardAction

    public static class CardAction.Builder
extends Object
    This class allows the construction of CardAction objects. To use, create a Builder instance, call its methods to populate the CardAction, and call build() to receive the completed CardAction and reset the builder.

    A CardAction can be discarded during creation, returning the Builder to its initial state, by calling reset(). The build() method calls reset() internally.
